N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 8189.21 - Saving clause

State Regulations

Nothing contained in this Part shall affect the validity of a
tax map approved by the State Board of Equalization and Assessment pursuant to
the said rules and regulations adopted by the State Board of Equalization and

Assessment on March 22, 1956 or prior thereto and the parcel identification
numbers on such maps used to describe real property on assessment and tax rolls
completed prior to January 1, 1984. Notes
